OL,3,CBeautician held in Chicago jail for
OL,4,Cdrug smuggling will be home in two
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FA beautician from Teesside has been
OL,8,Ftold she will now only serve a
OL,9,Ffraction of the 60-year sentence she
OL,10,Fhad feared for carrying two suitcases
OL,11,Fpacked with cocaine through Chicago's
OL,12,Fmain airport en route to Britain.
OL,14,FITV News understands Kimberley Hall
OL,15,Fcould now be back home in as little as
OL,16,Fa year but no longer than two years -
OL,17,Fonce final legal negotiations are
OL,18,Fcomplete.
