OL,3,CBeautician held in Chicago jail for
OL,4,Cdrug smuggling will be home in two
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FSpeaking after a plea bargain hearing
OL,8,Fin Chicago, her attorney Brandon
OL,9,FCarter said state prosecutors have
OL,10,Faccepted the 29-year-old was forced to
OL,11,Fcarry the drugs under duress while
OL,12,Falso suffering from bipolar disorder
OL,13,Fthat affected her decision making.
OL,15,FFinal sentencing in the case is now
OL,16,Flisted for 8th September 2025.
OL,18,FHer lawyer said Hall was delighted and
OL,19,Fexcited by the news and that she is
OL,20,Feager to get home.
